textContent:
---empty feeling---

Kakabalik lang namen galing airport bby huhuhu. Wala lang, sad huhuhu. Ang empty bigla ng feeling ng bahay. Nasanay naman kame kase more than 10 years na na ganito, pero it really never gets easier haaay. Ang hirap talaga maging magulang, you have to sacrifice your own happiness and joy for family. 

Naaawa ako sa papa ko kase ang saya saya talaga namen pag kumpleto kame, pero he has to give that up para lang maging comfortable kame sa buhay namen. I appreciate and love him for that so much huhuhu, I can't wait for the day na di na niya kailangan lumayo sa pamilya niya kase successful na mga anak niya and super comfortable na talaga sila. I'll do my best to be a good son talaga para maging comfortable mga magulang ko sa latter years nila, kase they really do deserve the best huhuhu.

And ofc, I'll also work hard for our future family!! Di naten kaya maghiwalay rugo HUHUHU jusko gumaga ku alang patugut. I'll work so hard para di na naten kailangan mag abroad ganern. O kaya kung mag aabroad man, dapat sabay talaga tayo dapat HAHAHAHW di ko rugo keri mahiwalay sa bunion bby ko HUHUHU.
